  [ -1 swap
    dup temp put
    bit times
     [ [] i^
       temp share times
         [ dup 1 &
           rot join swap
           1 >> ]
       swap witheach
         [ 1+ swap 10 * + ]
       dup prime iff
         [ nip conclude ]
         done
       drop ]
     temp release ]         is 1-2-prime ( n --> n )

  [] 20 times [ i^ 1+ 1-2-prime join ]
  witheach [ echo cr ]
